## 1. Project Overview

**CrossFriend** is an India-only e-commerce storefront for cakes, decor, gifts, costumes, and wellness products. The **AI Cake Studio** is a flagship feature that lets users generate AI cake design concepts from text prompts and selections, then convert those into real orders with local verified bakers.

**Live domain:** pranajiva.in

