| Frontend | Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion |
| Backend | Medusa V1 (JS client `@medusajs/medusa-js` v6.1.7) running on port 9001 |
| Auth | OTP-based (mobile → mapped to `{mobile}@pranajiva.in` email in Medusa) |
| Payments | Stripe, PayPal (configured but not AI Studio specific) |
