## 12. Price Estimator (`price-estimator.tsx`)

- Appears only after generation (`generated` prop)
- Collapsible accordion UI
- Loads config from `/api/ai-cake-studio-config` + live add-ons from `/api/cake-addons`
- Falls back to hardcoded config/add-ons if APIs fail
- Computes price from: base + weight + tiers + shape + style + flavor + options (eggless/express/midnight)
- Add-ons: suggested based on occasion+style, others in collapsible "More add-ons"
- Each add-on has: id, label, description, price, emoji, suggestFor, optional productId/variantId/thumbnail
- Grand total = base cake + selected add-ons
- CTA: "Find a Baker for This Price" scrolls to baker section

