## 13. Cake Add-ons API (`/api/cake-addons`)

- Queries Medusa for product category with handle `cake-addons`
- Fetches products in that category (expands variants + prices)
- Transforms to `Addon[]` using product metadata: `emoji`, `suggestFor` (comma-separated), `price` (₹ override)
- If no category exists or fetch fails, returns `{ addons: [] }` (graceful fallback)
- Price logic: metadata.price override → else cheapest variant amount ÷ 100 (paise → ₹)

