## 22. Important Design Decisions

- **India-only:** No multi-country routing; middleware simplified
- **Brand filtering:** All product/collection/category queries filter by `metadata.brand = "crossfriend"`
- **OTP over password:** Mobile-first auth; email is synthetic (`mobile@pranajiva.in`)
- **Counter vs Token:** UI says "attempts", backend uses "credits"
- **Graceful degradation:** All API calls have fallbacks; page never crashes if Medusa is down
- **Config-driven:** Pricing, selectors, and limits come from JSON config (editable without redeploy)

